 For intuition, consider a simple static example: there is one worker, his
 hourly rate 
\begin_inset Formula $p$
\end_inset

 is posted in advance but the costs across potential tasks are heterogenous.
 The worker's optimal strategy is to accept all tasks with cost below 
\begin_inset Formula $p$
\end_inset

